title: Bobby Is Nervous About Going To The Brain Doctor + The Sad Song Fantasy Draft + A Caller Asks Bobby On A Date

description:
Bobby talks about being nervous about an upcoming doctor’s appointment to get his brain checked out. We do our Sad Song Fantasy draft and Amy has the first pick. Bobby gave advice to a caller on getting a job…and she in turn asks him on a date!
